reviewText: This is one of the best Moose hunting DVD's I've ever seen!  It says over 90 mins and they're not lying!  It's not just 92 or 94 mins either.  It's like 140 mins of great moose footage not including the bonus hunts!  It's a nice mix of bow, rifle and muzzleloader hunts with really close up and fair chase hunts!  I highly recommend this product if you want to see some great Moose hunts!
